text: Syed Muhammad Fazal Agha (; (1946 â€“ 20 May 2020) was a Pakistani politician. He was Governor of Balochistan from August 18 to October 12 1999. He also was Deputy Chairman of the Senate of Pakistan from 1988 to 1991. from Balochistan. He was a member of the Provincial Assembly of Balochistan from 13 August 2018 till his death. Agha was born in Killi Huramzai, Pishin District.
